    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "ほな、午後は{user}さんを\nうちがずーっと、独り占めしてもええんちゃう？",
      "startTime": 3.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "今から二人きりで抜け出しましょ！",
      "startTime": 8.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "俺を独り占めって……それに、今から！？\nまだグラビア撮影は終わってないんだが……",
      "startTime": 16.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "機材の調整に、もう少しかかりそうやし\n終わったらスマホに連絡もらえばいいやんか",
      "startTime": 22.857846419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんとすみれちゃんとは遊びに行ったのに\nなんで、うちだけあかんの……？",
      "startTime": 29.457846419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "い、いや、優と一緒が嫌な訳じゃなくて……\n分かった、撮影再開するまで少しだけだぞ？",
      "startTime": 36.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "わ～、アイスクリーム、いろんな味がありますね\n{user}さんは何味にします？",
      "startTime": 48.662540245,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 43.3333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "あ、この味美味しそうやね。これ、一つください\nふふ、こういうとこでアイス食べるんは久しぶりやわ～",
      "startTime": 57.662540245,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……アイス食べるだけで、本当に良かったのか？",
      "startTime": 62.8625354131,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あんなに遊びに行きたがってたから\nてっきり海で泳ぐとか、買い物しまくるのかと……",
      "startTime": 68.9239117927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ。どんな無茶を言われるか\n気が気じゃなかった、って顔やね",
      "startTime": 76.1315199692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "うちだって、今が撮影中なのは分かってます\nいつ呼ばれるか分からんし、今はこれで我慢します",
      "startTime": 83.0315199692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、もし今日が丸ごとオフやったら……\n{user}さんをまず新幹線に乗せて……",
      "startTime": 90.7981866359,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（一体、俺に何をやらせるつもりだったんだろう……）",
      "startTime": 94.6648484707,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "今日は悪かったよ\nお詫びに、そのアイスは俺がおごるから",
      "startTime": 99.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "呆れた。あんな必死にうちの機嫌をとってたのに\nアイス代、うちに払わせるつもりやったんですか？",
      "startTime": 107.1789350509,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ご、誤解だ！　もちろん最初からそんなつもりは……",
      "startTime": 111.1122635524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、分かってますって",
      "startTime": 115.3857135456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "ところで{user}さん、気付いてました？\nうちの衣装だけ、ほら、ちょ～っと濡れてるんです",
      "startTime": 123.7857183774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "テストの時に、偉いカメラマンさんが\n少し濡れた方が色っぽいね～なんて言うたから",
      "startTime": 132.1322398754,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、その話をしてるのは俺も聞いてたよ",
      "startTime": 136.5190346719,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "聞いてたなら、褒めてくれてもええやないですか\nどうです？　うち、ちゃんと色っぽく見えますか？",
      "startTime": 144.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、夏っぽくて可愛いと思うぞ",
      "startTime": 148.7242189885,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "もう。それじゃ答えになってません\nうちは色っぽいかどうか聞いてるんです～",
      "startTime": 155.5412730694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そういうのはあまりおおっぴらに言うもんじゃ……\n……い、色っぽく見えるし、よく似合ってるよ",
      "startTime": 164.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、合格とはいきませんけど\n{user}さんにしては上出来やね",
      "startTime": 173.075072209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "あ、スタッフさんからスマホに連絡が\nそろそろ撮影再開するみたいだな",
      "startTime": 179.5333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 175.7333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "あーあ、もう少しお話したかったんやけどな～\nじゃあ、うちは戻ります",
      "startTime": 188.0318400541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "ずっとうちらの撮影中炎天下にいましたし\nもう少し休んでから来て下さい",
      "startTime": 194.4985128243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu019.m4a",
      "text": "撮影にアイス持って行く訳にもいかんし……\nせや、{user}さん、あーんして下さい",
      "startTime": 201.5985016346,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "あーんってどういうことだ？\nお、おい優！　食べかけを渡すんじゃない！",
      "startTime": 208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 212.85696311
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_03-yu020.m4a",
